---
title: Cheesy Tomato Orzo with Mozzarella & Bacon
description: Orzo is one of the tiniest pasta shapes out there - at first glance you might mistake one for a grain of rice. They make a great addition to soups and stews, but today we're letting them absorb some flavourful stock, a little like a risotto. An orzotto if you will. Enriched with bacon and not one but two types of cheese, it's a real treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-tomato-orzo-wk39-ec9966f7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/cheesy-tomato-orzo-wk39-df6361a8.pdf
servings: 2
